Third-party references used during driver development:

  * EG4 XP / kPV / FlexBOSS driver (vendors/eg4) — register map
    cross-referenced against three public sources, no code copied
    verbatim:
      - joyfulhouse/eg4_web_monitor (MIT) — register addresses
        and canonical Luxpower field names.
      - celsworth/lxp-bridge (MIT) — Luxpower-LXP semantics.
      - EG4 18kPV-12LV Modbus Communication Protocol PDF (EG4
        Electronics, publicly mirrored). Register definitions
        are facts, not creative expression, and so not subject
        to copyright.

  * Deye / Sunsynk / Sol-Ark driver (vendors/deye) — same
    research-then-clean-room shape, three public references:
      - kellerza/sunsynk (Apache-2.0) — primary Python register-
        map source for both single-phase and three-phase variants.
      - StephanJoubert/home_assistant_solarman (Apache-2.0) —
        Home Assistant integration, cross-reference for the same
        register definitions.
      - Deye Modbus protocol PDF (publicly mirrored at
        domotica.solar). Register definitions are facts, not
        creative expression.
